fields.name: Espresso Brazil Beans
fields.description: A strong and smooth coffee with a rich flavour and perfect crema. This single origin is intense and full-bodied with a caramel sweetness and hints of chocolate.

fields.name: Gold Roast Ethopia Beans
fields.description: A mild coffee with flavours of whiskey, cacao, tropical fruit with balanced acidity. These dense Ethiopian beans are not as intense but are still full of flavour.

fields.name: Signature Blend Columbian Beans
fields.description: Our famous signature Happy Bean blend is smooth and perfectly balanced, making it the perfect all-day drinking coffee. It has hints of a nutty flavour.

fields.name: Rich Roast Honduras Grounds
fields.description: This Rich Roast Ground Coffee is a darker roast with a rich, fruity flavour of Poached Peach, and it has a velvety consistency.

fields.name: Decaf Indonesia Grounds
fields.description: This is a smooth decaf Indonesian coffee with a medium strength profile. Some of the flavours that might come through are Chocolate Brownie and Cherry.

fields.name: Espresso Kenya Grounds
fields.description: This single origin Kenyan coffee is elegant and balanced with hints of berries and citrus fruits.

fields.name: Signature Blend Columbian Capsules
fields.description: Our famous signature Happy Bean blend in Compostable Coffee Capsules. This coffee is smooth and perfectly balanced with hints of a nutty flavour. This includes 30 capsules.

fields.name: Decaf Indonesia Capsules
fields.description: Our smooth decaf Indonesian coffee in Compostable Coffee Capsules. This coffee has a medium-strength profile with hints of Chocolate Brownie and Cherry. This includes 30 capsules.

fields.name: Filter Coffee Papers
fields.description: These thick, bonded filter papers contribute to the clarity of brewed coffee. Includes 40 filter papers.

fields.name: AeroPress Filters
fields.description: The Original AeroPress Micro-Filters for use in the AeroPress Coffee Maker. Includes 350 filter papers.

fields.name: Hario V60 Drip Scale
fields.description: The Hario V60 Drip Scale is one piece of kit that will help you emulate professional brewing at home. This scale is perfect for making V60, Chemex or any pour-over coffee.

fields.name: Aeropress Coffee Maker
fields.description: The AeroPress is a versatile method of brewing which has completely revolutionised coffee brewing and It is great because it is durable, travel-friendly and easy to clean.

fields.name: Hario Cold Brew Pot
fields.description: The Hario Cold Brew Pot is the easiest way to enjoy cold brew coffee at home. It has High-Quality Heatproof Glass, is Dishwasher safe and has a capacity of 1000ml.

fields.name: Chemex Brewer
fields.description: This beautifully designed coffee brewer makes a clean, flavourful and delicious cup of coffee. It is Heat resistant, non-porous glass with a stylish wooden collar that prevents burns while pouring.

fields.name: Rhinoware Hand Grinder
fields.description: It can be argued that, regardless of your brew method, a grinder is the most important piece of equipment in a coffee brewer's arsenal. This Rhinoware Hand Grinder has a 25g capacity.

fields.name: Baratza Encore Grinder
fields.description: The Encore is lauded by coffee experts as the best solution for those who wish to brew excellent coffee at home. This grinder consistently grinds for brew methods from espresso to French Press and everything in between.

fields.name: Taster Box 1
fields.description: Try out our Taster Box with 4 x 75g samples of coffees. Includes a variety of Espresso Brazil Beans, Signature Blend Columbian Beans and Decaf Indonesia Grounds.

fields.name: Taster Box 2
fields.description: Try out our Taster Box with 4 x 75g samples of coffees. Includes a variety of Gold Roast Ethiopia Beans, Rich Roast Honduras Grounds and Espresso Kenya Grounds.

fields.name: Gift Box 1
fields.description: Treat a fellow coffee lover with our Coffee Gift Box which includes 1 x Signature Blend Beans, 1 x Honduras Rich Roast Grounds and a card in a gift box.

fields.name: Gift Box 2
fields.description: Treat a fellow coffee lover with our Coffee Gift Box which includes 1 x Signature blend Capsules, 1 x Gold Roast Beans, 1 x Espresso Ground and a card in a gift box.
